Two county officials&nbsp;charged with abuse of office. &nbsp;Appearing&nbsp;before Maralal Principal Magistrate Richard Koech, Secretary Stephen Letinina and minister for Tourism Peter Leshakwet were charged that on November 1, 2014, they unlawfully awarded Africality Company a contract to manage Maralal Safari Lodge. They were released on a Sh300, 000 bond and hearing set for July 4 and 5.&nbsp;